'''穆罕默德·希达亚乌拉'''（{{lang-ur|محمد_ہدایت_اللہ}}，{{lang-en|Mohammad Hidayatullah}}，{{bd|1905年|12月17日|1992年|9月18日}}），出生于[[英属印度|英属印度]]、[[印度副總統列表|印度副總統]]和[[印度总统列表|代总统]]<ref name=VP-list>{{cite web|title=Former Vice Presidents of India|url=http://vicepresidentofindia.nic.in/former.asp|publisher=Secretariat of Vice President of India|accessdate=2014-09-03|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017115825/http://vicepresidentofindia.nic.in/former.asp|archivedate=2014-10-17}}</ref>。同时也是著名法学家、学者、教育家、作家和语言学家<ref name="full court-desai">{{cite journal|last1=Desai|first1=P. D., Justice|title=Full Court Reference in Memory of The Late Justice Mohammad Hidayatullah|journal=(1992) 4 SCC (Jour) 10|url=http://www.supremecourtcases.com/index2.php?option=com_content&itemid=99999999&do_pdf=1&id=543 |accessdate=2014-09-03}}</ref><ref name=Chagla>{{cite web|title=Speech by Shri I. M. Chagla|url=http://bombayhighcourt.nic.in/libweb/references/pdf/Justice%20Hidayatullah.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/19920928010101/http://bombayhighcourt.nic.in/libweb/references/pdf/Justice%20Hidayatullah.pdf|publisher=Bombay High Court|accessdate=2014-09-03|archivedate=1992-09-28|dead-url=yes|page=7}}</ref>。

